Package: qtl2helper
Type: Package
Title: Helper functions for R/qtl2 package
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Hugo", "Tavares",
                role = c("aut", "cre"),
                email = "hm533@cam.ac.uk")
Maintainer: Hugo Tavares <hm533@cam.ac.uk>
Description: qtl2helper provides helper functions to work with objects 
    created by several functions in the R/qtl2 package. Namely, it provides methods 
    for the `tidy` function (from the `broom` package), which convert those objects 
    to (long) data frames.
